# This fixture's member-declared unused-dependency mechanism needs a real
# (but hand-authored, never `npm install`ed) node_modules manifest — see
# labels.yaml's case description. The repo-root .gitignore excludes every
# "node_modules/" directory anywhere; these negations re-include only this
# fixture's own hand-authored one(s), at any depth under this directory.
!**/node_modules/
!**/node_modules/**
